accumulates the force of authority through the repetition or citation of a prior and authoritative set of practices}{\cf1\i0\b0\hich\af10\langfe255\dbch\af12\afs24\alang1025\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\lang255
. It is not simply that the speech act takes place within a practice, but that the act is itself a ritualized practice. What this means, then, is that a performative "works" to the extent that it }{\cf1\i\b0\hich\af10\langfe255\dbch\af12\afs24\alang1025\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\lang255
draws on and covers over}{\cf1\i0\b0\hich\af10\langfe255\dbch\af12\afs24\alang1025\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\lang255
